typeDescription.name: de.tudarmstadt.ukp.dkpro.core.api.lexmorph.type.pos.POS
typeDescription.description: The part of speech of a word or a phrase.

featureDescription.name: PosValue
featureDescription.description: The string representation of POS. Mostly it is the POS representation of the wrapped POS tagger.

typeDescription.name: de.tudarmstadt.ukp.dkpro.core.api.lexmorph.type.pos.tweet.AT
typeDescription.description: at-mention (indicates another user as a recipient of a tweet)

typeDescription.name: de.tudarmstadt.ukp.dkpro.core.api.lexmorph.type.pos.tweet.DM
typeDescription.description: discourse marker, indications of continuation of a message across multiple tweets

featureDescription.name: documentTitle
featureDescription.description: The human readable title of the document.

featureDescription.name: documentId
featureDescription.description: The id of the document.

featureDescription.name: documentUri
featureDescription.description: The URI of the document.

featureDescription.name: collectionId
featureDescription.description: The ID of the whole document collection.

featureDescription.name: documentBaseUri
featureDescription.description: Base URI of the document.

featureDescription.name: isLastSegment
featureDescription.description: CAS de-multipliers need to know whether a CAS is the last multiplied segment. Thus CAS multipliers should set this field to true for the last CAS they produce.

typeDescription.name: de.tudarmstadt.ukp.dkpro.core.api.metadata.type.ProcessorMetaData
typeDescription.description: Information about a CAS processor such as a reader, analysis engine, multiplier, or consumer.

featureDescription.name: instanceId
featureDescription.description: Unique identifier for this processor instance. If the same processor is applied multiple times to the CAS in different configurations, each application has a unique instance ID. In a clustered environment, each cluster node running a processor in a particular configuration should produce the same instanceId.

featureDescription.name: name
featureDescription.description: Name of the processor as per the 'name' field in the processor meta data.

featureDescription.name: version
featureDescription.description: Version of the processor as per the 'version' field in the processor meta data.

featureDescription.name: annotatorImplementationName
featureDescription.description: Java class implementing the processor.

featureDescription.name: splits
featureDescription.description: A word that can be decomposed into different parts.

typeDescription.name: de.tudarmstadt.ukp.dkpro.core.api.segmentation.type.Split
typeDescription.description: A part of a compound word.

featureDescription.name: category
featureDescription.description: The type of morpheme. (morpheme or linking-morpheme)

featureDescription.name: splits
featureDescription.description: Sub-splits of the current split.

featureDescription.name: parent
featureDescription.description: The parent of this token.

featureDescription.name: name
featureDescription.description: the name of the tag

typeDescription.name: de.tudarmstadt.ukp.dkpro.core.api.syntax.type.PennTree
typeDescription.description: The Penn Treebank-style phrase structure string

featureDescription.name: PennTree
featureDescription.description: Contains a Penn Treebank-style representation of a tree.

featureDescription.name: TransformationNames
featureDescription.description: The name(s) of the transformation(s) that have been performed on the PennTree

featureDescription.name: parent
featureDescription.description: The parent constituent

featureDescription.name: Governor
featureDescription.description: The governor word

featureDescription.name: Dependent
featureDescription.description: The dependent word

featureDescription.name: DependencyType
featureDescription.description: The dependency type

featureDescription.name: Cluster
featureDescription.description: Cluster assignment.

featureDescription.name: label
featureDescription.description: label

featureDescription.name: Origin
featureDescription.description: Typically something like 'Truth', or 'Prediction'

featureDescription.name: group_id
featureDescription.description: allows to distinguish between FCA along different instance and attribute sets.

typeDescription.name: de.uniwue.temine.uima.unittest.type.UnitTestFailed
typeDescription.description: Used to indicate that an assertion inside an analysis engine failed. Use its String parameter cause to pass messages.

typeDescription.name: org.apache.uima.examples.SourceDocumentInformation
typeDescription.description: Stores detailed information about the original source document from which the current CAS was initialized. All information (like size) refers to the source document and not to the document in the CAS which may be converted and filtered by a CAS Initializer. For example this information will be written to the Semantic Search index so that the original document contents can be retrieved by queries.

featureDescription.name: uri
featureDescription.description: URI of document. (For example, file:///MyDirectory/myFile.txt for a simple file or http://incubator.apache.org/uima/index.html for content from a web source.)

featureDescription.name: offsetInSource
featureDescription.description: Byte offset of the start of document content within original source file or other input source. Only used if the CAS document was retrieved from an source where one physical source file contained several conceptual documents. Zero otherwise.

featureDescription.name: documentSize
featureDescription.description: Size of original document in bytes before processing by CAS Initializer. Either absolute file size of size within file or other source.

featureDescription.name: lastSegment
featureDescription.description: For a CAS that represents a segment of a larger source document, this flag indicates whether this CAS is the final segment of the source document. This is useful for downstream components that want to take some action after having seen all of the segments of a particular source document.
